Hmm, it sounds like the `require('tablesorter')` isn't finding jQuery... I searched [Stack Overflow](https://stackoverflow.com/a/25978543/145346) and there's a recommendation to do the following:

```js
window.jQuery = require('jquery');
window.$ = window.jQuery;
require('tablesorter'); // it will attach itself to jQuery

$(function() {
  $('.table.sortable').tablesorter();
});
```

